  <brief_title>Teplizumab for Prevention of Type 1 Diabetes In Relatives &quot;At-Risk&quot;</brief_title>
  <official_title>AntiCD3 Mab (Teplizumab) For Prevention of Diabetes In Relatives At-Risk for Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
